tup\":[],\"agent_guidance\":\"For native-image runtime tests on JDK 25/current-defaults, set runtime system properties `-Dsun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow` and `-Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true`. Tests can use `Vertx.vertx()`, an in-process `HttpServer` bound to `127.0.0.1`/port 0, and `WebClient.create(...)`; no external service is required.\",\"risks\":[\"If generated tests choose OAuth2-specific APIs, `vertx-auth-oauth2` is optional in the POM and may require a deliberate dependency decision, but it is not needed for core WebClient coverage.\",\"The unsafe-access properties are a native/JDK-25 compatibility workaround; local Gradle and Native Image verification remain authoritative.\"]}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0883f47e23d1e90e016a4157462edc81939b6f8933c7b7161d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 6164, "output": 790, "cacheRead": 27136, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 34090, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782667066306, "responseId": "resp_0883f47e23d1e90e016a41573b1df08193a03b533f215cebf0"}, "toolResults": []}
